1
00:00:24,460 --> 00:00:26,300
It's a 9,000-year-old treasure from His Majesty

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:28,700
Even if you have 100 heads, it's not enough.

3
00:00:30,800 --> 00:00:32,000
Please spare my life.

4
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:34,400
That bitch splashed it on me!

5
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:36,130
I'm innocent!

6
00:00:39,730 --> 00:00:40,360
Minister ordered

7
00:00:40,360 --> 00:00:41,500
You take the opportunity to get promoted.

8
00:00:41,500 --> 00:00:42,400
and sneak into the Commandant's Office.

9
00:00:42,460 --> 00:00:43,360
If there is a chance,

10
00:00:43,360 --> 00:00:45,560
put this bag of poison in Ying Wudu tea.

11
00:00:46,400 --> 00:00:48,560
Yes, Your Majesty.

12
00:00:52,260 --> 00:00:53,130
Yu Henian.

13
00:00:53,660 --> 00:00:54,730
You want me to kill

14
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:55,660
the person I love the most.

15
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:56,660
Okay.

16
00:00:56,830 --> 00:00:58,300
I'll play along.

17
00:00:59,100 --> 00:00:59,700
for this.

18
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,100
I don't believe you've really become a useless person.

19
00:01:16,830 --> 00:01:19,300
The steward's nanny died of a sudden illness.

20
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:20,830
Minister said hello.

21
00:01:21,060 --> 00:01:22,330
From today on,

22
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,860
you will be transferred to the Wardrobe Service.

23
00:01:27,660 --> 00:01:29,130
Thank you, Prime Minister.

24
00:01:29,630 --> 00:01:30,900
Thank you for your promotion.

25
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,330
Minister said

26
00:01:32,330 --> 00:01:34,200
the Wardrobe Service is more convenient for you.

27
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,229
Don't forget your duty.

28
00:01:41,460 --> 00:01:43,200
My life was given by you.

29
00:01:43,400 --> 00:01:44,900
I know what to do.

30
00:01:45,430 --> 00:01:46,259
Take care, Eunuch.

31
00:01:52,060 --> 00:01:55,200
The Wardrobe Service gave me

32
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,330
to approach you.

33
00:02:00,160 --> 00:02:01,030
Why are you crying?

34
00:02:01,230 --> 00:02:02,730
As for the Commander of Eastern Depot,

35
00:02:02,930 --> 00:02:04,460
You're all hesitating.

36
00:02:04,660 --> 00:02:05,460
Are you disobeying the order?

37
00:02:06,660 --> 00:02:07,600
Madam, please spare my life.

38
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:09,500
Commander Ying killed without blinking.

39
00:02:09,660 --> 00:02:12,060
He cut Xiu'er's hand on the spot last month.

40
00:02:14,700 --> 00:02:15,700
Aunt, don't worry.

41
00:02:16,130 --> 00:02:18,260
I'll do it. I'll do it.

42
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:19,500
You...

43
00:02:20,630 --> 00:02:21,430
Jing Zhi.

44
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:23,329
That's the Eastern Depot.

45
00:02:23,730 --> 00:02:25,700
One careless move will kill you.

46
00:02:27,100 --> 00:02:29,530
I was born with my life.

47
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,700
It's my fate

48
00:02:32,030 --> 00:02:33,329
it's my fate.

49
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,400
So what?

50
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,260
It's not your fault.

51
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:40,860
Let's see how you can hide this time.

52
00:02:56,300 --> 00:02:56,700
Commander Wang.

53
00:02:56,700 --> 00:02:58,200
The Wardrobe Service sent someone

54
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,930
They are ordered to measure your clothes.

55
00:02:59,960 --> 00:03:01,030
He's waiting outside.

56
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:07,230
How dare you report such trivial matters to me?

57
00:03:07,230 --> 00:03:08,000
Send him away.

58
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:10,830
Just do it the same size.

59
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:13,000
Commander.

60
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:14,800
It's a new maid.

61
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,860
Her name is Qu Jing Zhi.

62
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:17,130
She said she couldn't see you.

63
00:03:17,130 --> 00:03:18,460
she hit her head and died at the door.

64
00:03:32,900 --> 00:03:33,760
Qu Jing Zhi.

65
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,930
Is she crazy?

66
00:03:36,530 --> 00:03:38,800
How dare she come to the Eastern Depot to die?

67
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,800
Since she wants to die,

68
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,200
let her in.

69
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,230
Take her to the study of the Superintendent Bureau.

70
00:03:52,860 --> 00:03:54,600
Yu Henian asked me to poison him.

71
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,160
but he didn't know

72
00:03:56,430 --> 00:03:59,360
what I hold is more fatal than poison.

73
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:01,230
It's not my fault.

74
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:02,700
In this life,

75
00:04:02,930 --> 00:04:05,700
I'll skin you, a fake eunuch.

76
00:04:26,560 --> 00:04:27,630
It's you again

77
00:04:28,260 --> 00:04:29,830
The Purification Room spared your life.

78
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,130
How dare you

79
00:04:31,130 --> 00:04:32,830
to approach me again and again?

80
00:04:35,330 --> 00:04:37,030
Under the order of the Palace Penal Service,

81
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:39,100
I'm here to measure the clothes for you.

82
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:42,530
My hand is a ruler.

83
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,430
Qu Jing Zhi.

84
00:04:50,860 --> 00:04:52,860
Be careful not to burn yourself.

85
00:04:55,659 --> 00:04:57,630
How do you know my name?

86
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,600
Look how guilty you are.

87
00:05:01,060 --> 00:05:04,260
Are you really a normal man?

88
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:09,730
Is it hard enough?

89
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:11,230
A dagger.

90
00:05:12,130 --> 00:05:16,030
It turns out that there's only a dagger on your waist.

91
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:17,700
It's not your fault.

92
00:05:18,400 --> 00:05:19,960
Did you really

93
00:05:20,500 --> 00:05:22,560
for me?
